body:
This does not seem to fix the issue in #16587.

Fresh virtualenv with tf 1.6 and h5py, `import tensorflow` yields:
```
/Users/alex/.virtualenvs/test3/lib/python3.5/site-packages/h5py/__init__.py:36: FutureWarning: Conversion of the second argument of issubdtype from `float` to `np.floating` is deprecated. In future, it will be treated as `np.float64 == np.dtype(float).type`.
  from ._conv import register_converters as _register_converters
```
